OL,3,CPositive first week for Salford-based
OL,4,CBBC News at One
OL,6,GIt is still early days for the
OL,7,Grevamped BBC News at One. But the
OL,8,Gearly indications are that the
OL,9,Gprogramme is proving a success.
OL,11,FAs I anticipated, the first half hour
OL,12,Fof the programme has barely changed `
OL,13,Fbeyond the move to Salford and the use
OL,14,Fof the Breakfast set.
OL,16,FEven so, the lack of a traditional
OL,17,Fdesk and the use of the Breakfast sofa
OL,18,Fis well disguised.
OL,20,FMany links are being presented from
OL,21,Fthe "tower" position. The sofa is not
OL,22,Fapparent in the tighter seated links.
