OL,6,FThe first obvious editorial change is
OL,7,Fat 1.30pm with a shorter weather
OL,8,Fforecast ` the main forecast has been
OL,9,Fmoved back to 1.55pm.
OL,11,FThe short forecast needs to have a
OL,12,Fclearly set editorial purpose. It
OL,13,Fshould be there to give a quick
OL,14,Fsummary of the forecast for the next
OL,15,Ffew hours for those who cannot stay
OL,16,Ftuned for longer ` it should not focus
OL,17,Fon the longer term forecast or the
OL,18,Fbackground. That can wait for half an
OL,19,Fhour.
