OL,6,FImmediately after the forecast, there
OL,7,Fhave been stories from BBC Verify and
OL,8,Fstudio chats. All fine but I can't
OL,9,Fhelp but feel that the regional opt
OL,10,Fshould come straight after the weather.
OL,12,FIn an ideal world, I would argue that
OL,13,Fthe nations and regions deserved a
OL,14,Flonger extension to the lunchtime
OL,15,Fbulletin.
OL,17,FI am sure the nations would have no
OL,18,Fdifficulty in producing, say, a 12-
OL,19,Fminute programme rather than a 10-
OL,20,Fminute one. But perhaps resourcing
OL,21,Fwould make this problematic in the
OL,22,FEnglish regions?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/7
