OL,6,FOf course, the election and coverage
OL,7,Fof the D-Day anniversary means that it
OL,8,Fis hard to truly get a sense of how
OL,9,Fthe extra time will be used routinely.
OL,10,FWhat will happen on a dull news day?
OL,12,FThe ratings suggest the new format is
OL,13,Fa success.
OL,15,FThe ratings for the first half hour
OL,16,Fand the regional opt seem normal `
OL,17,Fattracting about 2m viewers and around
OL,18,Fthree times the audience watching ITV
OL,19,F1.
