OL,6,FThe audience slips at 1.45pm ` perhaps
OL,7,Fbecause of people returning to work `
OL,8,Fbut the extra news is winning a bigger
OL,9,Faudience than Doctors gained in the
OL,10,Fslot.
OL,12,FAll in all, the team in Salford
OL,13,Fdeserve praise for such a strong and
OL,14,Fassured start.
OL,16,FAs things settle down, they will no
OL,17,Fdoubt get a stronger sense of how the
OL,18,Fextra time can be best used and look
OL,19,Fat whether a few tweaks are necessary.
